7 Vadam yadā pāpī jīvaḥ
8 tasya purastād āgacchati, sarvam ātmānam ācakṣate;
9 sa ca pāpavid jñātā

10 paśyati narakam yasya yogo 'syāḥ;
11 puccham ādadānaḥ tāvad āhatīḥ karoti
12 yāvad adhastād avatāraṇīyāḥ krameṇa bhūmayaḥ.

19 "paśya kathaṃ praviśasi kathaṃ ca viśvasasi;
20 praviśatiḥ prādurāsīṃ mā bhūḥ pramattaḥ!"
21 Evaṃ ca mama prabhuḥ tasmai: "Kimartham evam krośasi?

31 Narakātivātaḥ, yaḥkadācinnaśāmyati,
32 ātmānaḥsvakīyayābalenacodati;
33 parivartayanpariharyaṃścapidayati.

34 Yada āgacchanti puraḥ patanasya,
35 tatra krandanāni, vilāpāḥ, paridevanāni ca;
36 tatra devatāśaktim nindanti.

43 iha, tatra, adhaḥ, ūrdhvam ca nayati;
44 na āśā kadācid eva teṣāṃ sampravardhate,
45 kim uta viśrāmasya, kim uta alpīyasaḥ duḥkhasya.

49 chāyāḥ pūrvakathitena pravāheṇa nītāḥ;
50 yasmāt aham uvāca: "Bhagavan, ke naḥ ete
51 janāḥ yaṃ kṛṣṇavāyuḥ evam daṇḍayati?"

61 Anyā sā yā svayam eva ātmānam hanti kāmārtaḥ,
62 Sthāpayati ca viśvāsam Siceasya bhasmani;
63 Tataḥ paścāt kāmasukhāsaṅgatā Kleopatrā.

82 Yathā kāpotayo’bhilāṣeṇa āhūtāḥ
83 pakṣau utkṣipya sthirau ca madhuraṃ nīḍam prati
84 āgacchanti nabhasā, icchāyā niyamitāḥ;

127 Ekasmin dine vayam pathyāmahe ratihetave
128 Laṃkālaṭasya yathāpremaṇā saṃyujyate;
129 Eke vayam āsīma na ca kaścid āśaṅkā.
